Package com.petpet.c3po.command

This package contains all CLI commands.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Command A command interface for the CLI.
 

Class Summary
AbstractCLICommand An abstract CLI command that has some helper methods for implementing commands.
ExportCommand Submits an export to csv request to the controller based on the passed parameters.
GatherCommand Submits a gather meta data request to the controller based on the passed parameters.
HelpCommand Prints help messages for all supported modes of C3PO.
ProfileCommand Submits a profile request to the controller based on the passed parameters.
RemoveCommand Submits a remove request to the controller based on the passed parameters.
SamplesCommand Submits a samples generation request to the controller based on the passed parameters.
VersionCommand Prints the version information of c3po.
 

Package com.petpet.c3po.command Description

This package contains all CLI commands.
